Mutliple Columns:
\begin{multicols}{X} \end{multicols}                         # where X is the number of columns
\begin{multicols*}{X} \end{multicols*}                       # unbalanced columns
\setlength{\columnsep}{X}                                    # where x is a distance between columns.

\begin{wrapfigure}{l}{0.7\linewidth} [text] \end{wrapfigure} # wrapping figures with columns
\begin{wraptable}{l}{0.7\linewidth} [text] \end{wraptable}   # wrapping tables

\def\columnseprulecolor{\color{X}}                           # column separator

\columnbreak # for starting a new column
